    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for an urgent, linear power delivery up to its 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless; the rear subframe\u2014a known point of failure\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. The suspension remains tight with OEM-plus bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the original factory-spec geometry. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic over an unblemished Nappa leather interior, the vehicle exhibits zero oxidation on the undercarriage and impeccable paint depth. This is a mechanically sorted, purist-spec example ready for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 44900.0,
