    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom condition with absolutely zero compromises. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster, free from any swirls, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the chrome trim sparkles like new. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or bolster softening, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. All electronics, from the infotainment system to the climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been garage-kept and maintained strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule with all service records documented. It drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Included are both original keys, the full owner\u2019s manual set, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is an investment-grade example intended for the most discerning enthusiast.",
